Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜组装起来的 不要弄坏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 不要松手 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 "规则"是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(328,355)}{\fs20}Regulation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似于决定机器能否参赛的一种标准吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差距太大的话就称不上比赛了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego看上去像是市贩的量产型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面却有冈仓老师装的优化组件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(462,355)}{\fs20}Custom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架构跟外形就已经违规了 没法让它出赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 BALON和Fuego一样是特努强机动公司生产的新型号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系统也是一样的 小琳的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真服了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始不就告诉你要当心点的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 别闹了 快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Fuego的话就很不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力练习的奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这半个月的特训 你骑得不错了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算参赛也没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是比赛了 我会和你决个分晓出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定出任GGP治安维持部\N队司令官的罗曼洛夫·卡连巴古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已抵达横田基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周预定举行的就任仪式上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以首相为首的内阁官僚们将出席…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:58.73,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:58.73,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:03.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:03.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:14.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:14.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:21.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:21.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:08.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:08.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
